@node REGISTRAZIONE "Registration"


                                   @{b}REGISTRATION @{ub}

 FrontRay3 1.2 is a Shareware product, if you like it or use it frequently please to
 consider the registration.
 You will receive the last version of FrontRay without limitation and you will may load
 and save all parameters of your section in the file.proj

 If you have a @{"PGP key" link CHIAVEPGP} send it to me.

 @{i}Registartion by E-mail: @{ui}

     You will receive the program via E-mail.
     Specify "Registration E-Mail" in the your request and the Internet address where
     do you want i send the program.

 @{i}Registration by post:@{ui}

     You will receive the program by post in a 880k floppy-disk.
     Add $3 o 5DM at the registration fee for postage.
     Specify "Registration by post" in the your request and your complete name, surname
     and address.


 @{b}For the registration send $15 or 20 DM or eqivalent in other currency
 in a close envelope o by postal order to:@{ub}

            @{b}Ireneo Toffano
            Via Guerzoni 14
            35010 Cadoneghe - PD
            ITALY   @{ub}



@endnode

